    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty\u2014it\u2019s been incredibly reliable and still looks fantastic on the road! The interior is super clean, and it runs like a dream. It\u2019s definitely been well-cared for, showing just a little bit of character from normal use, but it's in really solid shape and ready for its next owner to enjoy. It would make a perfect daily driver for someone who wants a dependable ride that still feels special. Drop me a message if you want to come take it for a spin!",
