    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available now is a meticulously cared-for vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and everyday luxury. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like finish, though close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door\u2014typical signs of careful road use. The alloy wheels are in excellent shape with no significant curb rash, wrapped in tires with plenty of tread remaining. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery has been regularly conditioned to prevent cracking, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system and navigation, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change and a full brake service completed just last month. There are no warning lights on the dash and no unusual noises from the suspension or engine. This is a turn-key vehicle, perfect for a buyer who appreciates a car that has been respected and maintained with an open checkbook.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sophisticated styling. This unit has been maintained to a rigorous standard, ensuring a driving experience that remains both smooth and responsive. The exterior retains a distinguished luster, while the interior reflects a commitment to cleanliness and consistent care. For the discerning driver seeking a reliable, high-performing automobile that balances luxury with practical value, this offering represents an exceptional acquisition.",
      "price": 34900.0,
