      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape, runs super smoothly, and has been really well-loved. If you're looking for a reliable ride that still looks fantastic on the road, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home.",
      "price": 32500.0,
