    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a quintessential driver's machine powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This engine features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system, providing exceptional throttle response and a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a M-Variable differential lock for optimal power distribution. The chassis has been addressed with necessary subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. Though it exhibits typical wear for its age, the suspension geometry remains precise and the powertrain pulls strong through every gear. A perfect candidate for the purist seeking visceral performance.",
